 unbelievably slow. I've been playing for days and there are still things that are hidden from me and I have no idea what they do until I actually spend the 5-6 hours unlocking it. As a player, it's truly the only reason I keep this game thumbs down.Update 2: Got back into the game and tried some new things. Things ran smoother since I now know more, but the game still has so much information withheld from the player, even after 100+ hours I still haven't tried everything. It's simply too time consuming to be fun anymore and with the recent patch, there seems to be even more steps and buildings to build to do what you were able to do before without those steps and buildings. I haven't ever had the chance to charge the beacon and win the game even once. This game is dead to me, and I will not change my stance on it."
