 coded!Awesome!If you'd rather want things a bit more stable then don't opt into the Bleeding edge and you will be fine. Keep in mind however that this game is under developement and it's NOT a AAA+ development team behind it, but some indie dev which means this a true early access game.If you can't stand work in progress games, then you'd better wait untill it's more polished and done before you jump in :P// Rambling endTL;DRI've spent around 80hrs and will probably spend another 80 in it's current state (without any of the updates) which means it's worth EVERY CENT I've paid for it already!10/10 from me."
